## Self-validation protocol

Before marking any task done:

1. Run `{{VALIDATOR_CMD}}`. Tier 1 (diagnostics) must be clean.
2. Open {{TRUTH_SURFACE}}. Write one sentence about what it looks like now.
3. Verify each in-scope concern. (Lighthouse for performance/a11y; viewport screenshots for responsive; etc.)
4. Dispatch the verifier subagent (see `scripts/verify_prompt.md`). Tier 2 (independent eyes) must sign off.
5. Log the outcome in your iteration notes (or `decision_log.md` if the change was non-trivial).

## Session start

1. Open `PROJECT_PLAN.md` — the master checklist. Confirm the active workstream item; if none is active, picking the next item with the user IS the first task. All work this session must map to an item there (add it first if missing).
2. Run the dev server:
```
{{DEV_SERVER_CMD}}
```
3. Verify state: `{{STATE_LOCATION}}` exists and isn't corrupted. Drift surfaces to spot-check: {{DRIFT_SURFACES}}.

